<p>This week's film: teaching a model to coach the way you would, by training one of your own. It pairs with the <a href="/how-to-build-an-ai/build-your-own-model/">Build your own model</a> chapter below.</p>

<p>Hi, and welcome. If you're curious how an AI actually gets built, and whether <em>you</em> could build one, this is a good place to start. This guide grows a chapter at a time, and you can read it at your own pace. You don't need any coding experience, and you don't need to finish all of it. Think of it as a gentle on-ramp, not a test.</p>

